{"tid":271317,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Wargame兇殺案】證人認出三被告 首被告或申請保釋","createTime":"2017-06-05T03:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T05:27:27.000Z","uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8bdd8139458c4efc580af042c9ce957f5092c4","tid":271317,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:44:52.000Z","msg":"20歲wargame迷郭葦諾於藍田五桂山疑遭謀殺案，案件今早再提堂。控方指3名被告已於認人手續中全部被認出，申請將案押後以等待驗屍報告、及政府鑑證等方面的調查。<br />\n<br />\n三被告依次為冷氣技工黃朗祺（21歲）、地盤工嚴汝衡（27歲）及海事處小輪助理周正賢（21歲），他們由警方押送到庭，三人在警車內均戴上頭套。<span style=\"color: red;\">黃今由大律師石書銘代表</span>，嚴及周由同一外籍當值律師代表。<br />\n<br />\n控方庭上指，案件上次押後期間，證人進行認人程序，已認出全部三名被告。控方仍需時等候調查報告及鑑證等結果。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">石書銘稱首被告或有意向高等法院申請保釋，要求法庭下令控方提供其餘被告的警誡口供等文件，以便全面檢視控方指控有否偏頗之處。裁判官以調查未完成為由拒絕，並將案押後至8月8日再訊，三人繼續還柙。</span><br />\n<br />\n控罪指三人於5月28日，在五桂山某處謀殺郭葦諾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n Link: <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170605&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56785186\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170605%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56785186&d=xp3lZiKZAHy2tdDJ6o9mdxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=8ffe1576\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170605%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56785186&h=5fa892fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170605&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56785186</a>"},{"pid":"befeee981719497b60c57fce1379ac84fe11a468","tid":271317,"uid":53244,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:48:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>遭票控切線 法政匯思大狀自辯打甩<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20161206/s00007/21e4fbcddbe235dfeca93c102c5b4937.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20161206%2Fs00007%2F21e4fbcddbe235dfeca93c102c5b4937.jpg&h=f5286e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊 2016/12/6】法政匯思成員、大律師石書銘今年5月駕車上庭途中被交通警員截停票控「橫過附有虛線的連續白線」。石昨否認控罪並親身抗辯，裁判官同意石的陳辭指警員證供粗疏，更質疑警員未有如實記錄切線位置，事後嘗試更改掩飾過錯，並非可靠證人，裁定石脫罪。"},{"pid":"153ad9ef52b2823965b8535244b3023db2be1269","tid":271317,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:49:27.000Z","msg":"就咁睇控告謀殺是咪好易打成誤殺? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bfea5fe99101e17c849d8b1d5beebc23e5548a","tid":271317,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"其實highlight石書銘個名有咩意思？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c49bfd3fd57481114986b54ec2b6ec4fc21e281","tid":271317,"uid":53244,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T04:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實highlight石書銘個名有咩意思？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請得起大律師是咪好易打甩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 唔熟法律"},{"pid":"9f849d899cb646383b55ee7f9de3cc4fa305e22d","tid":271317,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T04:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/mulicia/1375244963-2599818482_n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fmulicia%2F1375244963-2599818482_n.png&h=ca683708&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba49c016e14097f144661a3ff6a510cd6fdf5a84","tid":271317,"uid":97979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T04:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實highlight石書銘個名有咩意思？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請得起大律師是咪好易打甩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 唔熟法律</blockquote><br />\n大律師同律師唔係大與小的分別，大律師係訴訟律師，謀殺案肯定係大律師去打<br />\n真係有錢會請資深大律師，駱應淦同清洪嗰類"},{"pid":"a7f014893c38244009e643214dad344068b0d168","tid":271317,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T04:13:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55ed0b1ff02362eaec1a6b06e0c4be42c94d